Description: Fragment of strap handle at neck join of a Knidian pottery transport amphora. Clay near fine light red-brown. Rectangular stamp with trident symbol.
Type series: KT (629 - Virginia Grace's unpublished K(nidian) T(ype) series)
Bibliographic references: Stoddart 1847 / Memoir on the inscribed pottery of Rhodes, Cnidus and other Greek Cities (321)
